Share.d:
This project will give you multiple ways of automatically or semi-automatically toggle the dark mode on your Android 10 device.

Check out the demo video here: https://youtu.be/DpEIBgGLFNA.

IMPORTANT: You need Tasker 5.8.4 for this to work. Sign up for the beta here if needed.

Share.d:
Little task that will allow you to check the current screen orientation value on demand.
Orientations: - 0° (portrait) - 90° (landscape right) - 180° (upside down) - 270° (landscape left)
Notes: - The 180° rotation position may be locked by your ROM if not custom when using auto-rotation feature. So, try using Tasker to force that rotation angle or install a compatible custom ROM.

Action.label:
getOrientation(): Alternative, but deprecated method, which is actually called from the newer one 'getRotation()'.
(both should output same values)

Action.Str: Dont forget to pay for school!
